CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 10, 1962, pg. 5, reads: "Drive for Jobs - Shown above are the members of the NAACP Labor and Industry Committee. Left to right: Matt English, Mal Goode and James McCoy, co-chairmen, and Jack Wright Jr. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Members of NAACP Labor and Industry Committee, from left: Matt English, Mal Goode, James McCoy, and Jack Wright Jr., standing behind two signs reading "Let's Share Job Wealth" and "Lets All Have a Fair Share Jobs"
